            <TimelineText>
              <ul class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                <li>
                  <p class="mb-2 text-primary">
                    <strong class="text-white"
                      >Team leader of Astra project</strong
                    >. A new platform designed for students, teachers, and
                    administrative users, built using <strong class="text-white"
                      >React</strong
                    >. Responsible for implementing architecture, documentation,
                    authentication system, logs reporting and additional
                    features.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <Skill type="frontend">React</Skill>
                    <Skill type="backend">.NET Web API</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">C#</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">TypeScript</Skill>
                    <Skill type="database">IBM DB2</Skill>
                    <Skill type="database">PostgreSQL</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">HTML5</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">CSS3</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">Tailwind</Skill>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p class="mb-2 text-primary">
                    Built a <strong class="text-white"
                      >loan installment calculation system</strong
                    >. The system calculates interest, the number of
                    installments, total payments made, and the remaining
                    balance, all in accordance with the amortization schedule.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <Skill type="fullstack">.NET Framework</Skill>
                    <Skill type="database">IBM DB2</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">HTML5</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">CSS3</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">Javascript</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">C#</Skill>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p class="mb-2 text-primary">
                    Developed a <strong class="text-white"
                      >Syllabus System</strong
                    > for the University. Managed course information, including details
                    about teachers, class content, knowledge objectives, skills to
                    develop, and book authors related to the class content.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <Skill type="fullstack">.NET Framework</Skill>
                    <Skill type="database">IBM DB2</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">HTML5</Skill>
                    <Skill type="frontend">CSS3</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">Javascript</Skill>
                    <Skill type="programmingl">C#</Skill>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p class="mb-2 text-primary">
                    Participated in the <strong class="text-white"
                      >database migration</strong
                    > from <strong class="text-white">IBM DB2</strong> to <strong
                      class="text-white">PostgreSQL</strong
                    > by converting procedures, tables, triggers, and views into
                    PostgreSQL.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <Skill type="database">IBM DB2</Skill>
                    <Skill type="database">PostgreSQL</Skill>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p class="mb-2 text-primary">
                    Developed a comprehensive <strong class="text-white"
                      >consultation system for psychologists</strong
                    >. Designed and implemented the database, enabling the
                    tracking of patient history and consultations. Implemented a
